# Component Usage Guide

You can use @notionpresso/react components as follows:

```typescript
import { NotionRenderer } from '@notionpresso/react' // remove react-notion-custom

const BlogPost = ({ content }) => {
  return (
    <NotionRenderer content={content} />
  )
}

